production-grade full-stack web applications and websites with Vue.js.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>JavaScript 中的 async/await</title><link>http://localhost:1313/post/learn-frontend/javascript-es7-async-await/</link><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 10:29:27 +0800</pubDate><guid>http://localhost:1313/post/learn-frontend/javascript-es7-async-await/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;async/await&lt;/code&gt; 是基于 Promise、以同步方式编写异步代码的语法糖。&lt;/p&gt;
